39
00:03:55,248 --> 00:03:56,248
Okay.

40
00:04:01,048 --> 00:04:02,748
Miwako. Did I keep you waiting?

41
00:04:02,748 --> 00:04:03,748
I'm sorry.

42
00:04:03,748 --> 00:04:05,348
I sure did.

43
00:04:05,348 --> 00:04:07,948
I mean, it's your treat today, okay?

44
00:04:07,948 --> 00:04:10,848
What? I mean, I always treat you, don't I?

45
00:04:10,848 --> 00:04:12,748
Did you say something just now?

46
00:04:12,748 --> 00:04:14,548
No, I didn't.

47
00:04:15,948 --> 00:04:18,948
So shall we get going, then?

48
00:04:18,948 --> 00:04:19,948
I guess so.

49
00:04:28,848 --> 00:04:31,548
Put the money in this briefcase.

50
