66
00:05:18,148 --> 00:05:20,948
Well, I'm sorry to have kept you waiting.

67
00:05:23,548 --> 00:05:25,248
Are you Mr. Ishida?

68
00:05:25,248 --> 00:05:26,448
Yes.

69
00:05:26,448 --> 00:05:28,448
