70
00:05:28,448 --> 00:05:29,948
I'm so sorry.

71
00:05:32,448 --> 00:05:35,948
I'm sorry everyone, for making you wait.

72
00:05:35,948 --> 00:05:38,248
Okay, since everyone's on board,

