79
00:06:04,248 --> 00:06:06,248
Would you like a pamphlet?

80
00:06:06,248 --> 00:06:07,848
Thank you.

81
00:06:07,848 --> 00:06:10,048
"Spring Cherry Blossom Viewing Cruise"

82
00:06:12,948 --> 00:06:14,848
But, inspector...

