00:07:45,848 --> 00:07:48,548
We're waiting right across Eitai River.

113
00:07:48,548 --> 00:07:50,548
We confirmed with the cruiser company

114
00:07:50,548 --> 00:07:54,448
and found that it's supposed to go from Sumida River to Ooyoko River.

115
00:07:54,448 --> 00:07:57,748
You two go on ahead to Ooyoko River.

116
00:07:57,748 --> 00:07:58,748
Roger.

117
00:08:01,448 --> 00:08:02,748
Wow. How wonderful.

118
00:08:02,748 --> 00:08:04,248
Amazing.

119
00:08:07,648 --> 00:08:10,648
It's about time you start working for me.

120
00:08:10,648 --> 00:08:13,748
That cruiser is headed for Oojima water gate

121
00:08:13,748 --> 00:08:15,548
and will be going into Ooyoko River.

122
00:08:15,548 --> 00:08:20,048
Then, put the briefcase on the roof of the cruiser.

123
00:08:20,048 --> 00:08:22,448
Put it in the center so that it doesn't fall.

