138
00:09:18,148 --> 00:09:19,148
What did you say?

139
00:09:20,148 --> 00:09:22,648
The briefcase is on the roof.

140
00:09:36,948 --> 00:09:38,348
It's impossible to pull the briefcase

141
00:09:38,348 --> 00:09:40,748
up from the bridge in this crowd people.

142
00:09:40,748 --> 00:09:41,948
Besides...

143
00:09:45,948 --> 00:09:49,448
With so many surveillance cameras all over the place, the more so.

144
00:10:07,148 --> 00:10:08,448
Did you wait long?

145
00:10:12,148 --> 00:10:13,148
That was close.

